1. Jaeger 설정
    wget https://download.jaegertracing.io/v2.16.0/jaeger-2.16.0-linux-amd64.tar.gz
    tar zxvf jaeger-2.16.0-linux-amd64.tar.gz
    cd jaeger-2.16.0-linux-amd64
    ./jaeger --set=receivers.otlp.protocols.http.endpoint=0.0.0.0:4318

2. 그라파나 및 프로메테우스
    1. 프로메테우스
      1) 기존 프로메테우스 제거
        sudo systemctl stop prometheus
        sudo systemctl disable prometheus
        sudo systemctl unmask prometheus
        sudo apt remove prometheus -y
        sudo rm -f /etc/systemd/system/prometheus.service
        sudo rm -f /lib/systemd/system/prometheus.service
        sudo systemctl daemon-reload

      2) 최신 버전 다운 및 설치
        wget https://github.com/prometheus/prometheus/releases/download/v3.10.0/prometheus-3.10.0.linux-amd64.tar.gz
        tar zxvf prometheus-3.10.0.linux-amd64.tar.gz
        cd prometheus-3.10.0.linux-amd64
        sudo cp prometheus /usr/local/bin/
        sudo cp promtool /usr/local/bin/
        sudo mkdir -p /etc/prometheus /var/lib/prometheus

      3) 설정
        vi /etc/prometheus/prometheus.yml
            안에 내용 다 삭제
            global:
              scrape_interval: 5s
              evaluation_interval: 5s

            scrape_configs:
              - job_name: 'spring'
                metrics_path: '/actuator/prometheus'
                scrape_interval: 5s
                static_configs:
                  - targets:
                      - '192.100.200.100:8080'   # Spring Boot 앱 IP:포트

        vi /etc/systemd/system/prometheus.service
            [Unit]
            Description=Prometheus 3.8.1
            After=network.target

            [Service]
            User=root
            ExecStart=/usr/local/bin/prometheus \
              --config.file=/etc/prometheus/prometheus.yml \
              --storage.tsdb.path=/var/lib/prometheus \
              --enable-feature=exemplar-storage
            Restart=always

            [Install]
            WantedBy=multi-user.target

        sudo systemctl daemon-reload
        sudo systemctl start prometheus
        sudo systemctl status prometheus

    2. 그라파나
      1) 설치
    	wget -q -O /usr/share/keyrings/grafana.key https://packages.grafana.com/gpg.key
    	echo "deb [signed-by=/usr/share/keyrings/grafana.key] https://packages.grafana.com/oss/deb stable main" | tee -a /etc/apt/sources.list.d/grafana.list

    	apt update
    	apt -y install grafana


